files.content:
#data entry 
studid=input("Student ID :")
fname=input("Fullname:")

#writing text file
stud=open("record.txt","a+")

stud.write(f"Student ID: {studid} \n")
stud.write(f"Fullname: {fname} \n")
stud.close()
stud=open("record.txt","r")
print("Press any to continue to display records...")
input()
print(stud.read())
stud.close()
